WEBVTT

00:00.202 --> 00:01.256
Where do you work?

00:01.839 --> 00:05.751
I work for ABC Limited as a software engineer.

00:06.641 --> 00:10.383
It's a good job for me because I like working with computers.

00:11.278 --> 00:12.263
How about you?

00:12.901 --> 00:14.161
I'm a journalist.

00:14.867 --> 00:19.686
I interview people and write stories for a famous American newspaper.

00:20.042 --> 00:22.084
What do you do in your free time?

00:22.971 --> 00:25.267
At the moment, I'm learning Italian.

00:25.991 --> 00:27.659
It's fun but difficult.

00:28.457 --> 00:29.428
How about you?

00:30.042 --> 00:31.775
I like to go rock climbing.

00:32.499 --> 00:36.395
It's good exercise and I can enjoy the fresh air too.

